title: The Girl Down the Street | S1E1
description:
In the series premiere, young Felicia meets a new neighbor, prompting her mother to move them halfway across the country. Years later, a strange girl named Zoe inspires the same reaction, and Felicia finally learns of a horrifying family secret. This episode contains adult language.
~~
